claim.claim-text:
1. A battery module with a case having a battery cell housed therein, comprising:
a metal terminal having a fixing piece provided with a through hole, and extending from said case;
an insulator insulating said metal terminal and said case from each other; and
a rivet;
said insulator having a ring-shaped protrusion inserted in a through hole provided through said case,
said rivet fixing said fixing piece to said case through said through hole of said fixing piece and said ring-shaped protrusion of said insulator.
